item.title: Can someone help me with this error! and maybe some way to run a rsps please!?
item.dc:creator: @Infernal_Pure Infernal Pure
item.description:
@Infernal_Pure wrote:

That’s an error stating that the batch file can’t find the server.class

Meaning, if you don’t have server.java, there’s no server.class.

Look and see if you have server.java, if you don’t I recommend downloading a new source, and since you’re new, a beginner source. Look in the download section here - moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?board=49.0

Hope I helped (:
